# Compass Project Memory

## Project Overview
Student self-reflection platform. Students do structured sessions every 3 weeks → AI synthesizes into signal profiles → counselors get dashboard. Turborepo monorepo.

## Stack
- `apps/web` — Next.js 14 app router, deployed on **Vercel**
- `apps/ai-service` — FastAPI Python, deployed on **Railway**
- `apps/mobile` — React Native (untouched)
- `packages/db` — Prisma ORM + pg driver, Supabase PostgreSQL
- Clerk auth (roles: student/counselor/admin via publicMetadata)
- Upstash Redis (caching) + QStash (background jobs)
- Anthropic claude-sonnet-4-6 for synthesis, Voyage AI for embeddings (1024-dim)
- pgvector on MapNode.embedding for semantic similarity search

