## Railway AI Service Setup
- Root directory must be set to `apps/ai-service` in Railway settings
- Watch paths: `apps/ai-service/**`
- Port: 8000
- Env vars needed: ANTHROPIC_API_KEY, VOYAGE_API_KEY, DATABASE_URL (direct, port 5432), AI_SERVICE_SECRET_KEY, APP_URL
- Vercel needs: AI_SERVICE_URL (no trailing slash), AI_SERVICE_SECRET_KEY (same value)

## Vercel Env Vars Needed
- DATABASE_URL, DIRECT_URL (Supabase)
- NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY, CLERK_SECRET_KEY, CLERK_WEBHOOK_SECRET
